    "body": "I don't think the sum of the modified fees has any meaning. They are used to prioritize individual transactions (and thus their packages) for mining. It is not a fee that can be redeemed in any way and in most cases it will be an arbitrary number.\r\n\r\nThough, if they are added they can be called `total_modified_fee`, without breaking any clients. I'll leave as is for now.",
